        <updateDate>2020-11-17T20:25:19Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>SOS: Sustaining Outpatient Services Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows for payment under the Medicare prospective payment system for hospital outpatient department services of certain items and services that are furnished at off-campus outpatient departments. Specifically, the bill allows for payment of items and services for which payments to physician specialists (under the Medicare physician fee schedule) did not exceed $2 million during the previous year.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
